00:41.675 --> 00:43.077
Look,

00:43.111 --> 00:45.513
it hasa secret place.

00:45.546 --> 00:48.616
What goes in there?

00:51.185 --> 00:53.754
One day, Simon...

00:53.787 --> 00:56.624
You will know.

01:00.628 --> 01:03.431
You must stay truein your heart.

01:11.672 --> 01:14.208
Thank you, Jesus.

02:27.681 --> 02:29.450
