02:29.483 --> 02:30.584
Boy: yeah, I know.

02:30.618 --> 02:31.819
Is the bagin the car?

02:31.852 --> 02:33.721
Uh, yeah,it's in the front.

02:33.754 --> 02:36.190
You two don't planon moving all that stuffyourselves, do you?

02:36.224 --> 02:38.426
Hi, Mrs. rousso.

02:38.459 --> 02:41.128
No, my brother'smoving company is comingout here.

02:41.161 --> 02:45.499
We're just checkingto make sure nothing'smissing.

02:45.533 --> 02:47.401
I do my bestto keep an eyeon the place,

02:47.435 --> 02:49.837
but it's goodto double-check.

02:49.870 --> 02:52.873
