( Birds chirping )

09:41.248 --> 09:45.953
( Students chattering )

09:53.727 --> 09:55.796
- I'm so sorry.- It's okay.

10:03.336 --> 10:04.872
I'm Jake.

10:04.905 --> 10:06.840
This is David.

10:06.874 --> 10:09.609
I'm...i'm Anna.

10:09.643 --> 10:12.012
And this is Cindy.

10:12.045 --> 10:14.715
Hey, I know you.You help me in math class.

10:18.085 --> 10:20.287
You're beautiful--i mean--

10:20.320 --> 10:22.022
that's beautiful

10:22.055 --> 10:24.925
the fact that

10:24.958 --> 10:26.827
both of our friendsare in the same math class.

10:26.860 --> 10:29.963
Cindy: that's right.

10:29.997 --> 10:33.734
- Are you new here?- Yeah. I just moved herefrom California.

10:33.767 --> 10:35.936
Listen, we gotta getto class for some prep.

10:35.969 --> 10:37.037
See you later, okay?

10:37.070 --> 10:39.072
Yeah, okay.

10:39.106 --> 10:40.841
See you.

10:46.847 --> 10:48.816
Hey, you boys playingwith wooden blocks now?

10:48.849 --> 10:50.751
( Laughs )

10:50.784 --> 10:52.953
Listen,you know that girl

10:52.986 --> 10:54.755
that you werejust talking to?

10:54.788 --> 10:56.656
Well, I'm interested.

10:56.690 --> 10:59.626
So back off.

10:59.659 --> 11:00.894
Got it?

11:06.133 --> 11:07.367
( Spits )

11:14.975 --> 11:17.644
- So you stillhave that box?- Yeah.

11:17.677 --> 11:19.747
Jake, I don't thinkyou should talk to Anna.

11:19.780 --> 11:22.015
I'm not afraidof him, David.

11:22.049 --> 11:25.185
In fact,

11:25.218 --> 11:27.420
I think I'm gonna eatwith Anna in the cafeteriatomorrow.

11:27.454 --> 11:28.722
Oh no.

11:28.756 --> 11:30.123
Now i'mhaving visions.

11:30.157 --> 11:31.759
- Really?- yeah.

11:31.792 --> 11:33.160
Of you gettingyour butt kicked.

12:07.127 --> 12:09.329
( Shouting in foreign language )

12:20.140 --> 12:21.708
( Shouts )

12:24.111 --> 12:27.014
Man: why have you forsaken me?

12:32.986 --> 12:35.355
- Good morning.- Morning, mom.

12:39.526 --> 12:40.994
Jake, what'sin your backpack?

12:41.028 --> 12:42.262
My books.

12:42.295 --> 12:44.231
Doesn't soundlike books to me.

12:44.264 --> 12:45.933
Oh.

12:45.966 --> 12:47.901
You mean the box.

12:47.935 --> 12:51.972
I have grandpa's boxin there.

12:52.005 --> 12:55.809
Go ahead, open it.

12:55.843 --> 12:58.912
You already askedme this, Jake.

12:58.946 --> 13:00.280
Okay.

13:06.286 --> 13:08.521
( Sighs )nothing. I don't feelanything.

13:11.024 --> 13:12.192
Never mind.

13:17.931 --> 13:21.301
- I gotta go.- Jake, should I makean appointment for you?

13:21.334 --> 13:23.036
Are youfeeling okay?

13:23.070 --> 13:24.972
To what?

13:25.005 --> 13:27.540
A doctor?

13:27.574 --> 13:30.010
I'm fine.

13:30.043 --> 13:32.145
I told you.

13:32.179 --> 13:34.414
I'm gettingthese really weird feelingswhen I open the box.

13:34.447 --> 13:37.250
Yesterday, I opened it,and I saw a vision

13:37.284 --> 13:38.785
of a little boyholding it,

13:38.818 --> 13:40.120
in a different placein time.

13:44.858 --> 13:46.393
What do youmean, Jake?

13:46.426 --> 13:47.995
Are you sure?

13:48.028 --> 13:49.863
Yeah.

13:49.897 --> 13:51.198
Like the old times.

13:54.434 --> 13:56.536
No, don't evenstart thinking that.

13:56.569 --> 14:00.107
No. I'm not on drugs.

14:00.140 --> 14:01.808
And no,

14:01.841 --> 14:03.276
I'm not crazy.

14:11.184 --> 14:13.153
Hey, Anna.Have you seen David?

14:13.186 --> 14:15.222
No, I thought he'dbe with you...

14:15.255 --> 14:16.823
Is something wrong?

14:16.856 --> 14:19.059
Maybe he's stillin the lunch line?

14:25.398 --> 14:27.901
Jake, what are youdoing here?

14:27.935 --> 14:30.237
Aren't you goingto say hi to Anna?

14:30.270 --> 14:32.906
Jake, you knowwhat's going to happen,you're asking for it.

14:32.940 --> 14:34.341
I won't bea part of this.

14:34.374 --> 14:36.109
I'll see you later.

14:38.378 --> 14:39.612
What's wrong with him?

14:39.646 --> 14:41.381
What's goingto happen?

14:42.916 --> 14:44.351
I don't know.

14:44.384 --> 14:46.987
Maybe he'shaving a bad day.

14:47.020 --> 14:48.989
What do you havein there, Jake? Rocks?

14:52.259 --> 14:54.161
Jake: there's something I wanna show you.

14:54.194 --> 14:55.395
Anna: oh okay.

14:58.898 --> 15:02.936
( Spits )

15:02.970 --> 15:04.871
- Jake: what's going on here? - Anna: Oh boy.

15:04.904 --> 15:06.373
Jake: oh, it's Richie.

15:06.406 --> 15:08.341
- Hey, Richie.- You don't listen too well,

15:08.375 --> 15:09.642
do you, white boy?

15:11.544 --> 15:14.948
Do you guys wannasit with us?

15:14.982 --> 15:16.549
Why don't you comehave lunch with me, Anna?

15:19.019 --> 15:22.389
( Overlapping shouting )

15:24.958 --> 15:27.027
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

15:27.060 --> 15:29.029
Hey! hey!

15:29.062 --> 15:31.331
You got a situation here?

15:31.364 --> 15:33.133
Okay, you two downto the office, now!

15:33.166 --> 15:34.534
Now! now!

15:34.567 --> 15:37.237
Everybody calm down.The situation is okay.

15:37.270 --> 15:38.238
I've got your backpack.It's okay.

15:38.271 --> 15:39.539
Finish your lunches.

15:39.572 --> 15:41.008
Now!

15:41.041 --> 15:42.375
Principal: let's go!

15:48.081 --> 15:50.350
So what'sgoing on you guys,what's the deal?

15:50.383 --> 15:53.253
We don't havea deal, sir.

15:53.286 --> 15:55.455
So you guysboth know the consequencesfor fighting at school,

15:55.488 --> 15:58.191
- don't you?- Yes, sir.

15:58.225 --> 16:00.994
That's why I neverfight in school, sir.

16:01.028 --> 16:03.130
We weren'tfighting, sir.

16:03.163 --> 16:05.598
It was justa misunderstanding.

16:05.632 --> 16:07.667
That's notwhat it looked like

16:07.700 --> 16:10.103
from acrossthe cafeteria.

16:10.137 --> 16:13.306
Okay?

16:13.340 --> 16:15.175
Kids don't normally gatheraround like that

16:15.208 --> 16:17.377
unless there'ssome sort of altercationgoing on.

16:17.410 --> 16:20.147
And if you remember,i pulled you two offof each other.

16:20.180 --> 16:22.282
Now do I haveto pull out the rulebook

16:22.315 --> 16:24.417
so you two can startmemorizing all the rulesaround here?

16:26.453 --> 16:28.921
Or...

16:28.955 --> 16:30.523
Maybe we haveour own little,"breakfast club?"

16:35.562 --> 16:40.167
"The breakfast club"?It's a John Hughes film.

16:40.200 --> 16:42.335
Molly ringwald...

16:42.369 --> 16:43.703
A cool moviefrom the '80s

16:43.736 --> 16:47.307
about a bunch of kidsin detention.

16:50.610 --> 16:52.112
Nothing?

16:53.480 --> 16:55.482
We don't dodetention here.

16:55.515 --> 16:58.351
But I won't hesitateto suspend either oneof you guys

16:58.385 --> 17:00.520
if I seeany more problems.

17:00.553 --> 17:03.356
Do I makemyself clear?

17:03.390 --> 17:05.291
- Got it.- Yes, sir.

17:05.325 --> 17:07.627
I've got my eyeon you.

17:07.660 --> 17:10.163
Okay?both of you.

17:10.196 --> 17:12.199
One on you,and the other on you.

17:14.134 --> 17:16.502
All right,get out of here.Both of you guys.

17:16.536 --> 17:18.003
And I don't wanna seeyou in my office

17:18.037 --> 17:19.638
for the restof the year.

17:26.113 --> 17:28.080
Better watchyour back, white boy.

17:30.250 --> 17:33.686
Jake.

17:33.720 --> 17:37.324
You know, I heardabout your grandfather.

17:37.357 --> 17:41.494
He was always interestedin how you were doingin school.

17:41.528 --> 17:44.464
And he would alwayswant you to do your best.

17:44.497 --> 17:45.698
I know.

17:47.234 --> 17:49.336
Have a good day, Jake.

17:49.369 --> 17:51.638
One more thing.

17:51.671 --> 17:53.173
Did David tell youthere was somethinggoing on

17:53.206 --> 17:56.543
between me and Richie?

17:56.576 --> 17:58.778
Get to class, Jake.

18:31.678 --> 18:34.614
You just couldn't waitto get me in trouble,huh, Jake?

18:34.647 --> 18:37.550
Your little snitch friendhad to go and tellthe principal.

18:37.584 --> 18:41.154
What? do you thinki told David to goget the principal?

18:41.188 --> 18:42.822
Look, Richie,believe it or not,

18:42.855 --> 18:45.358
we're not afraidof you or your friends.

18:45.392 --> 18:48.628
Oh, you're not afraid?That's it you're askingfor it, white boy.

18:48.661 --> 18:52.432
Then why do you alwayshave to have all theseguys around you?

18:52.465 --> 18:55.067
Do you pay these guysfor protection or what?

18:55.101 --> 18:56.436
- That's it!- Leave it alone

18:56.469 --> 18:57.570
get off me, man.

18:57.604 --> 18:59.539
( Overlapping shouting )

18:59.572 --> 19:02.074
Get off me man!

19:02.108 --> 19:03.376
Come on,give that back!

19:03.410 --> 19:05.778
- Come on!- ( Laughing )

19:05.812 --> 19:07.680
Hey! give that back!

19:07.714 --> 19:09.716
Jeez! come on!

19:09.749 --> 19:11.150
( Booms )

19:27.334 --> 19:28.601
Come on, guys.Let's go.

19:43.683 --> 19:45.352
He saw it.

19:51.558 --> 19:54.361
Look at that.Man can't even get a cupof coffee around here

19:54.394 --> 19:56.363
without missingall the action.

20:00.833 --> 20:02.769
Yes, sir.

20:02.802 --> 20:04.504
Have a nice day.

20:05.538 --> 20:08.341
Jake.

20:08.375 --> 20:09.942
I'm here to help.

20:24.757 --> 20:27.560
What's up, Richie?What's bothering you?

20:27.594 --> 20:29.596
You haven't saida word since I got here.

20:29.629 --> 20:31.831
That box

20:31.864 --> 20:35.568
that Jake hadwith him today.

20:35.602 --> 20:36.903
When I opened it,

20:36.936 --> 20:39.672
I got a weird feelingall over me.

20:39.706 --> 20:41.274
What kindof weird feeling?

20:41.308 --> 20:44.877
I had a visionof a boy

20:44.911 --> 20:47.280
- behind a rock, crying.- Oh, yeah.

20:47.314 --> 20:49.682
My mom gets those,only she calls themhot flashes.

20:49.716 --> 20:51.884
Dude,

20:51.918 --> 20:53.386
listen to what I'm saying.

20:53.420 --> 20:55.322
( Video game beeps )

20:55.355 --> 20:56.689
Not like that.

21:00.259 --> 21:03.229
I had a peaceful feelingall over me.

21:05.798 --> 21:09.702
I felt good.

21:09.736 --> 21:11.270
I thinki'm just gonnahave to stay away

21:11.304 --> 21:13.506
from that guy.

21:13.540 --> 21:15.274
What are your plansfor today, Jake?

21:15.308 --> 21:16.343
Anything special?

21:16.376 --> 21:18.445
Nothing really.

21:18.478 --> 21:20.447
Gonna meet upwith David and we're gonnago to the mall later

21:20.480 --> 21:22.782
and shoot some hoops.They're having an open gymlater.

21:22.815 --> 21:26.653
I think they're recruitingplayers for the team,

21:26.686 --> 21:30.357
but me and davidare just gonna shootsome hoops.

21:30.390 --> 21:32.725
Oh, I have a friendcoming over tonight.

21:32.759 --> 21:34.861
Oh, anyone I know?

21:34.894 --> 21:36.563
No, her name's Anna,she's helping me with somehomework.

21:38.731 --> 21:40.800
Should I order youand Anna some pizzafor dinner?

21:40.833 --> 21:42.502
Yeah, that'dbe great.

21:42.535 --> 21:45.672
