Hey, buddy, wanna playsome one-on-one?

22:22.742 --> 22:24.343
- Gym's open till 7.- Let's go.

22:28.581 --> 22:30.950
By the way, no cryingwhen you lose, punk.

22:33.886 --> 22:35.522
Shut upand play, snitch.

23:00.112 --> 23:02.949
Hey, Anna's comingover later tonight.

23:02.982 --> 23:05.351
Oh, so you didcall her.

23:05.384 --> 23:08.387
- Are you gonnashow her the box?- Aw, shoot.

23:08.421 --> 23:10.457
I was gonna bring itso you could see itone more time.

23:10.490 --> 23:12.324
You just don't stop,do ya?

23:12.358 --> 23:14.093
Look Jake,i can't seewhat you see

23:14.126 --> 23:15.728
or feelwhat you feel.

23:15.762 --> 23:18.498
Maybe Anna will.

23:18.531 --> 23:20.767
