23:20.800 --> 23:22.435
Why can't you?

23:22.469 --> 23:24.604
I don't know, buddy.

23:24.637 --> 23:27.006
I don't knowwhy I can't see it,or why I can't feel it.

23:27.039 --> 23:29.108
Maybe I'm notsupposed to.

23:29.141 --> 23:32.779
I don't know.

23:32.812 --> 23:35.114
It's just keepingme up at night.

23:35.147 --> 23:36.749
I don't knowwhat to do with it.

23:36.783 --> 23:38.551
All right, well tell mehow it goes, all right?

23:38.585 --> 23:41.721
- You aren't coming?- No, three's a crowd.

23:41.754 --> 23:43.756
And besides,you have to showher the box.

23:43.790 --> 23:46.058
Maybe she can help you.

23:46.092 --> 23:47.627
