23:47.660 --> 23:50.497
You said you seejesus, right?

23:50.530 --> 23:52.164
Maybe he's tryingto tell you something.

23:52.198 --> 23:55.802
Maybe he wants youto go back to church again,jake.

23:55.835 --> 23:57.537
Yeah.

23:58.738 --> 24:00.473
Whatever.

